---
import { Sparkles, Leaf, PlayCircle } from '@lucide/astro';
---

<section class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-24">
  <div class="grid items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
    <!-- Left Content -->
    <div class="fade-in-section">
      <div
        class="mb-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-gray-900/10 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900"
      >
        <Sparkles class="h-4 w-4" />
        Our Story
      </div>
      <h2 class="mb-6 text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 md:text-4xl">Built for a Better Planet</h2>
      <p class="mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-800/80">
        Waste Wise Innovation began in 2023 with a simple question: <strong
          >How can we help people recycle right at the bin?</strong
        >
      </p>
      <p class="mb-8 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-800/80">
        What started as fieldwork at major events in 2022 evolved into a team of sustainability
        experts, engineers, operators, strategists, educators, and mentors designing smarter
        recycling technology.
      </p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gray-900">
          <Leaf class="h-6 w-6 text-white" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Waste Wise Innovation</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Revolutionizing recycling since 2023</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right Visual -->
    <div class="fade-in-section" style="transition-delay: 200ms;">
      <div class="glass-panel rounded-[2rem] p-8">
        <div
          class="mb-6 flex aspect-video cursor-pointer items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-gray-100 transition-transform hover:scale-[1.02]"
        >
          <PlayCircle class="h-20 w-20 text-gray-700 transition-transform hover:scale-110" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">See Topper Stopperâ„¢ in Action</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Watch how our technology is transforming recycling programs across the country.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
